snippet.title: Amber Heard  Textbook Narcissist Traits
snippet.description:
*A couple times I said "broke the NDA," when discussing Johnny going to meet Amber in San Francisco...I  meant to say "Restraining order."  Forgive me for saying the wrong terminology.  I'm tired today, haha.
Johnny Depp, in his texts to Christian Carino, described Amber Heard as having "textbook Narcissist Traits."  Her pathetic attempts to gaslight him and the situation are not ending anytime soon, but my hope is, on March 23rd, she is exposed in earnest for who and what she truly is.
A Textbook Narcissist.
